♪A woman with three suitors♪

252
00:11:45,376 --> 00:11:47,936
♪They say I'm fickle♪

253
00:11:48,224 --> 00:11:50,656
♪The scholar confesses all with drinks♪

254
00:11:50,752 --> 00:11:52,832
♪The guard just gives her a stony face♪

255
00:11:54,001 --> 00:11:56,372
♪The regent waits in the moonlight♪

256
00:11:56,544 --> 00:11:58,601
♪The title
of Empress Dowager brings pity♪

257
00:11:59,584 --> 00:12:01,921
♪Palace farces play daily♪

258
00:12:02,486 --> 00:12:04,642
♪Endless plot twists♪

259
00:12:05,211 --> 00:12:07,550
♪That glimpse of you that day♪

260
00:12:07,744 --> 00:12:09,933
♪Made my heart flutter♪

261
00:12:10,272 --> 00:12:11,264
♪Peach blossoms♪

262
00:12:11,488 --> 00:12:12,736
♪Bloom one by one in my heart♪

263
00:12:13,088 --> 00:12:14,112
♪Who do I love♪

264
00:12:14,112 --> 00:12:15,552
♪I guess with no direction♪

265
00:12:16,288 --> 00:12:17,280
♪Who's pretending♪

266
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:19,008
♪While the truth slips by♪

267
00:12:19,072 --> 00:12:21,352
♪Pretense becomes true as years flow♪

268
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,525
♪Dawn bells wake the dreamer♪

269
00:12:24,928 --> 00:12:27,473
♪Sunlight bathes crimson walls♪

270
00:12:27,949 --> 00:12:30,176
♪You said meeting me♪

271
00:12:30,272 --> 00:12:33,571
♪Was your most beautiful surprise♪

272
00:12:33,571 --> 00:12:35,296
♪Peach blossoms♪

273
00:12:35,584 --> 00:12:38,432
♪Whose heart do they touch♪

274
00:12:38,907 --> 00:12:39,904
♪Love resides within you♪

275
00:12:39,904 --> 00:12:41,590
♪It brings sweetness to us two♪

276
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:42,496
♪My heart races♪

277
00:12:42,496 --> 00:12:44,416
♪In this life, we refuse
to pass by as strangers♪

278
00:12:44,416 --> 00:12:46,560
♪Lovers shall share
the moon's eternal grace♪

